Package: EVAstatobsR
Title: Verification of (regional) reanalyses with station measurements
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: person("Michael", "Borsche", email = "michael.borsche@dwd.de",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A verification package of global (ERA20C and ERA_Interim) and
    regional (COSMO-REA6 HErZ) reanalyses against German station data. In this
    first installation, only windspeed data is analysed. Monthly and daily time
    series are compared; correlations, historgrams, scatter plots, PDF-score,
    and many more metrics are calcualted and plotted.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.2),
    ncdf,
    ncdf.tools,
    xts,
    vioplot,
    RCurl,
    fitdistrplus
License: GPL (>=3)
LazyData: false
